---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Signario"
  description="How Signario collects, uses, and protects your personal data."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p>
            Signario ("we", "our", "us") is an AI-powered customer feedback management tool for B2B product teams.
            Our website is <a href="https://signario.io" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">signario.io</a>.
            For privacy questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@signario.io" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">hello@signario.io</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Data we collect on this website</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">On the signario.io marketing website, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Email address</strong> — when you submit the waitlist form. Used only to contact you about early access.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Analytics data</strong> — page views and click events via PostHog, only if you accept cookies. Data is anonymised and aggregated.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not sell, rent, or share your email address with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            We use cookies only for analytics (PostHog). A cookie consent banner is shown on your first visit.
            If you decline, no tracking cookies are set. You can change your preference at any time by clearing
            your browser's local storage for signario.io.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Third-party services</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Web3Forms</strong> — processes waitlist form submissions and forwards them to our inbox. See <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Web3Forms Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-slate-300">PostHog</strong> — analytics, only with your consent. Data stored in the EU (Frankfurt, Germany). See <a href="https://posthog.com/privacy" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PostHog Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Vercel</strong> — website hosting. See <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vercel Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
          <p>If you are in the EU/EEA, you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To exercise these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@signario.io" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">hello@signario.io</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Data retention</h2>
          <p>Waitlist email addresses are retained until you request deletion or the waitlist closes. Analytics data is retained per PostHog's default retention policy (1 year).</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy as the product evolves. Material changes will be communicated via email to waitlist members. The "Last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent revision.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@signario.io" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">hello@signario.io</a>.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
